    example: "During the Sinulog festival in Cebu, devotees perform a two-steps-forward, one-step-back dance mimicking the river's current, while holding their Santo Nino images aloft. The nine-day novena preceding the feast fills the basilica to overflowing, with Masses celebrated around the clock.",
