    body: "Devotion to Divine Providence is the practical expression of faith in God's sovereign governance of the world. Jacques Philippe teaches that trusting Providence is the heart of interior peace: God permits nothing that He cannot turn to good for those who love Him. This devotion involves daily acts of trust, accepting unforeseen events as permitted by God, and resisting the anxiety that comes from trying to control the future.",
